1
00:00:14,359 --> 00:00:15,080
Come here.

2
00:00:15,080 --> 00:00:16,120
Brother, don't go.

3
00:00:16,199 --> 00:00:17,760
Let go of my brother, kiddo.

4
00:00:25,359 --> 00:00:26,760
Stop crying, stop crying.

5
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:27,680
You're awake, Captain Li.

6
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:30,799
Here.

7
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:32,719
Have some water.

8
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:44,400
How are you feeling?

9
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:48,040
Sorry about that, Dr. Meng.

10
00:01:49,159 --> 00:01:50,120
I've been a bit tired lately.

11
00:01:52,959 --> 00:01:53,760
Dr. Meng.

12
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:57,599
Brother Li's vitals are basically normal.

13
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:59,079
His lung function is good too.

14
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:00,959
I told you I'm fine.

15
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:03,680
Your brother insisted I get checked out.

16
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,239
Captain Li.

17
00:02:06,879 --> 00:02:09,599
Normal vitals don't mean you're really okay.

18
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:13,479
Come by for some hypnotic induction sometime.

19
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:17,599
It'll help ease your pain and improve sleep.

20
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:20,599
For a detective,

21
00:02:21,879 --> 00:02:23,400
pain-free moments are pretty rare.

22
00:02:24,879 --> 00:02:25,680
I've got things to do.

23
00:02:26,479 --> 00:02:27,199
I'm heading out.

24
00:02:27,479 --> 00:02:28,000
Hey.

25
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:29,520
See you, Ruolan.

26
00:02:29,639 --> 00:02:30,199
Bye-bye.

27
00:02:32,039 --> 00:02:32,919
Take care, Captain Li.

28
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:42,800
Sometimes I really admire detectives like your brother.

29
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:45,879
The mental pressure they bear

30
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:49,199
is far greater than ours.

31
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:09,080
Boss, just let me go in and take a look.

32
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,840
You saw how I did yesterday.

33
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:12,319
I didn't let you down at all.

34
00:03:15,159 --> 00:03:16,560
You sure you won't embarrass me?

35
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:19,560
What? You're underestimating me.

36
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:21,439
Even if I had to perform the autopsy myself,

37
00:03:21,599 --> 00:03:22,560
I wouldn't be scared one bit.

38
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:27,680
Let's go!

39
00:03:51,319 --> 00:03:51,919
Scared, are you?

40
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:54,800
No.

41
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,639
I'm just observing.

42
00:03:57,560 --> 00:04:01,159
Boss, what is Forensic Doctor Sun doing?

43
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,520
Team Two still has no leads on the case.

44
00:04:07,039 --> 00:04:09,000
Thirteenth time simulating the suspect's crime.

45
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,479
He's already destroyed three dummies.

46
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:11,840
Never seen this before?

47
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:15,159
I've seen it all.

48
00:04:17,319 --> 00:04:19,839
Okay, this is actually a first.

49
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:22,480
It's freezing in here, but you're sweating.

50
00:04:22,759 --> 00:04:24,160
You're a bit weak, aren't you?

51
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:26,000
What? Me, weak?

52
00:04:27,399 --> 00:04:28,399
And you say you're not.

53
00:04:28,399 --> 00:04:29,279
Your legs are shaky.

54
00:04:30,519 --> 00:04:31,959
Rule of the forensic lab:

55
00:04:32,399 --> 00:04:34,079
Don't touch the autopsy table.

56
00:04:47,759 --> 00:04:48,800
The bone slice examination revealed

57
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:51,040
heavy hemoglobin staining in the victim's bone canaliculi,

58
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,800
consistent with being hit by a car while still alive.

59
00:04:54,639 --> 00:04:56,519
That ditch isn't far from the highway.

60
00:04:56,879 --> 00:04:58,279
Liu Xiang must have run onto the highway

61
00:04:58,279 --> 00:04:59,600
and got hit while seeking help.

62
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:19,120
The suspect saw Liu Xiang was dead,

63
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,319
and to avoid responsibility,

64
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:24,000
he dumped her in Liuye Lake.

65
00:05:41,399 --> 00:05:44,040
But why did the suspect strip Liu Xiang naked?

66
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:54,759
Liu Xiang didn't die immediately after the impact.

67
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:57,040
The sexual assault happened while she was still alive.

68
00:05:57,879 --> 00:06:00,199
Since the body was submerged for a long time,

69
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,680
the swelling in her lower body wasn't obvious.

70
00:06:02,319 --> 00:06:03,480
We only found it during the autopsy.

71
00:06:04,079 --> 00:06:06,000
But no usable biological traces were recovered.

72
00:06:07,959 --> 00:06:09,480
Was the fatal injury caused by the impact?

73
00:06:09,959 --> 00:06:11,480
Based on the location of the injuries,

74
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:12,480
yes, it was the impact.

75
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:13,800
Look here.

76
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,680
There's an impact wound on her head,

77
00:06:18,959 --> 00:06:20,160
which caused intracranial hemorrhage.

78
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:22,439
And look at this.

79
00:06:25,519 --> 00:06:26,439
Occipital hematoma.

80
00:06:27,399 --> 00:06:28,399
This kind of occipital hematoma

81
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:30,000
is usually caused by a vehicle hitting from the side-rear

82
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,720
or directly from behind.

83
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,160
The bathroom's on the right.

84
00:06:43,519 --> 00:06:44,680
He held out this long.

85
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:46,879
Way better than my first time seeing a corpse.

86
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,160
With some training, this kid

87
00:06:50,279 --> 00:06:51,560
has what it takes to be a detective.

88
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:55,639
The Stone-Faced Judge learned how to compliment people?

89
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,720
Don't I usually compliment you?

90
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,199
My dear Sun Scalpel.

91
00:07:09,759 --> 00:07:12,319
Normal sedans hit the waist or below,

92
00:07:12,839 --> 00:07:14,759
so occipital hematoma is unlikely, right?

93
00:07:15,279 --> 00:07:16,600
You should've become a forensic doctor.

94
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:18,399
Generally speaking,

95
00:07:18,399 --> 00:07:20,759
only an impact from a flat, tall front

96
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:22,279
would create an occipital hematoma.

97
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,399
Judging from her injuries,

98
00:07:24,879 --> 00:07:26,600
the best match would be a van,

99
00:07:26,879 --> 00:07:28,279
or a small flat-front truck.

100
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:31,600
Organ and intracranial hemorrhage suggest

101
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:33,639
the time from impact to death

102
00:07:33,639 --> 00:07:35,000
shouldn't have exceeded one hour.

103
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:36,519
In other words,

104
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:39,680
she died during the sexual assault.

105
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:41,720
What an animal.

106
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:43,439
I've been a forensic doctor for years,

107
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:44,959
and this is the first time I've seen this.

108
00:07:45,199 --> 00:07:47,079
Hard to imagine someone vicious enough

109
00:07:47,399 --> 00:07:49,079
to treat a critically injured woman

110
00:07:49,079 --> 00:07:50,680
with such beastly cruelty.

111
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:55,399
Hey, Boss.

112
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:06,920
Why are you hiding?

113
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:10,399
Your hands are the classic powerful type.

114
00:08:12,279 --> 00:08:13,879
It helps ease the nausea and tension.

115
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,720
My first autopsy,

116
00:08:18,879 --> 00:08:20,000
I threw up worse than you did.

117
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:22,519
Later my teacher told me something.

118
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:26,079
If a forensic doctor can't face the dead,

119
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,439
they can't uncover the truth.

120
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:31,160
Ever seen someone not react to a corpse?

121
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,679
Anyone human has a reaction.

122
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:36,039
But some naturally control it better.

123
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,240
Like your boss.

124
00:08:37,559 --> 00:08:38,720
If he were a forensic doctor,

125
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,120
he'd be much better than me.

126
00:08:42,519 --> 00:08:43,240
Looks like

127
00:08:43,639 --> 00:08:45,159
my boss really is a jack-of-all-trades.

128
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:49,519
We first met in the forensic lab.

129
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:51,679
He asked me,

130
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,840
"What's the duty of a forensic doctor?"

131
00:08:54,759 --> 00:08:57,080
I said, "Let the dead speak,

132
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:58,080
defend the rights of the living."

133
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:00,279
I asked him about a detective's duty.

134
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,879
He said, "Let the living find peace,

135
00:09:03,399 --> 00:09:04,519
let the dead rest in peace."

136
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:07,799
That sounds a bit contradictory.

137
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:10,120
That's what I said back then too.

138
00:09:10,879 --> 00:09:12,639
He said in uncovering truth from a body,

139
00:09:12,799 --> 00:09:13,480
there's no contradiction.

140
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,799
Whoever holds the scalpel calls the shots.

141
00:09:16,399 --> 00:09:17,080
Eat up.

142
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,759
Stop! Stop the car!

143
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:10,440
Stop!

144
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,399
The night she was killed,

145
00:10:11,679 --> 00:10:12,320
Stop!

146
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:14,960
Liu Xiang must've sought help on the road.

147
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:17,759
But no one stopped.

148
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:21,240
Then she was hit by a van.

149
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:06,159
The driver didn't call the police or help

150
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:08,639
most likely because

151
00:11:08,879 --> 00:11:10,120
he was driving drunk.

152
00:11:11,799 --> 00:11:13,679
He thought the victim was already dead,

153
00:11:14,559 --> 00:11:16,639
panicked, and loaded her into the car.

154
00:11:29,879 --> 00:11:32,080
He chose to dump the body at Liuye Lake,

155
00:11:33,879 --> 00:11:35,039
which most likely means

156
00:11:36,559 --> 00:11:38,440
his home or his destination

157
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:41,120
isn't far from there.

158
00:11:46,679 --> 00:11:47,240
Captain Li.

159
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:49,679
Tech Department used security footage

160
00:11:49,679 --> 00:11:51,200
to carefully analyze the highway

161
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,279
and surrounding routes near the scene.

162
00:11:52,799 --> 00:11:54,360
Based on the vans recorded on that road

163
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:55,759
and info on small trucks,

164
00:11:55,759 --> 00:11:58,279
we compared features, times, and routes,

165
00:11:58,399 --> 00:11:59,679
and narrowed it down to a few vehicles.

166
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:00,919
Excellent.

167
00:12:01,159 --> 00:12:01,919
Bro Wang, Fang Ping,

168
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:03,679
based on Lin Xue's compiled info,

169
00:12:03,679 --> 00:12:05,320
split up and investigate thoroughly.

170
00:12:05,480 --> 00:12:06,919
Remember, this must stay covert.

171
00:12:06,919 --> 00:12:08,120
Don't tip off the suspect

172
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,159
and let him slip away.

173
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:09,840
Yes, sir.

174
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:15,600
Back to the office.

175
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:17,480
Compile today's leads right away.

176
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:18,080
Got it.

177
00:12:23,039 --> 00:12:23,519
Okay.

178
00:12:23,919 --> 00:12:24,600
Thanks.

179
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:25,279
No problem. Bye.

180
00:12:25,279 --> 00:12:25,919
Ruolan,

181
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:27,639
your brother called you a bunch of times.

182
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:28,720
Call him back right away

183
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:29,720
and see what's up.

184
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:31,679
Sure, okay. Thank you, Dr. Meng.

185
00:12:34,399 --> 00:12:35,039
Hello, bro.

186
00:12:35,159 --> 00:12:36,519
You didn't forget what tomorrow is, right?

187
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:38,600
Hmm, what day?

188
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:40,240
Aren't they all good days?

189
00:12:40,440 --> 00:12:42,559
Just focus on your case.

190
00:12:42,799 --> 00:12:44,919
No way, it's only once a year.

191
00:12:45,759 --> 00:12:46,480
By the way, bro,

192
00:12:47,159 --> 00:12:49,399
I saw the rape case on the news.

193
00:12:49,759 --> 00:12:51,080
I know you're under a lot of pressure,

194
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:53,039
but you have to take care of yourself.

195
00:12:53,159 --> 00:12:54,320
You can't go without sleep.

196
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,240
Alright, I know.

197
00:12:56,559 --> 00:12:57,840
Just take care of yourself.

198
00:12:58,360 --> 00:12:59,919
Wait for me at work tomorrow.

199
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:02,879
I'll buy you your favorite mousse cake.

200
00:13:03,159 --> 00:13:04,320
Really, you don't have to.

201
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:06,399
Just focus on your work.

202
00:13:06,759 --> 00:13:07,600
You kiddo,

203
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:10,240
always thinking of others since childhood,

204
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:11,480
caring about everyone else's feelings.

205
00:13:13,399 --> 00:13:14,840
I've broken my promise two years in a row.

206
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,720
I have to make it up tomorrow night.

207
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:17,960
It's settled.

208
00:13:18,759 --> 00:13:19,399
Alright then.

209
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:21,759
I'll wait at the clinic tomorrow night.

210
00:13:23,039 --> 00:13:23,600
Okay.

211
00:13:28,159 --> 00:13:28,759
Boss.

212
00:13:28,919 --> 00:13:29,679
How's the case going?

213
00:13:30,039 --> 00:13:31,240
The investigation teams are all deployed.

214
00:13:31,399 --> 00:13:32,879
Jiang Han and I are going to see Feng Bing.

215
00:13:33,559 --> 00:13:34,159
Okay.

216
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:44,039
Tell me! Hurry up and tell me!

217
00:13:44,399 --> 00:13:46,000
Which bastard killed Xiang Xiang?

218
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:46,720
Tell me!

219
00:13:46,919 --> 00:13:47,519
It was you.

220
00:13:49,759 --> 00:13:50,879
It wasn't me.

221
00:13:51,399 --> 00:13:52,519
It really wasn't me!

222
00:13:53,159 --> 00:13:55,039
You said I didn't strangle Xiang Xiang!

223
00:13:55,039 --> 00:13:56,000
How could it be me?

224
00:13:56,519 --> 00:13:58,240
I loved her. I loved her so much.

225
00:13:58,240 --> 00:14:00,360
Do people like you deserve to say "love"?

226
00:14:00,879 --> 00:14:02,360
Liu Xiang catered to your every whim.

227
00:14:02,919 --> 00:14:03,919
And how did you treat her?

228
00:14:05,039 --> 00:14:06,039
Your mind was full of selfishness,

229
00:14:06,039 --> 00:14:07,440
possessiveness, twistedness, perversion.

230
00:14:07,639 --> 00:14:09,240
One wrong word and you'd beat her.

231
00:14:09,879 --> 00:14:10,799
Quite the tough guy, huh?

232
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,279
Beating up a woman.

233
00:14:13,039 --> 00:14:13,879
No.

234
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:18,000
I hit her to be a good wife and mother!

235
00:14:18,279 --> 00:14:19,279
Your so-called love

236
00:14:19,679 --> 00:14:20,919
was treating her kindness toward you

237
00:14:20,919 --> 00:14:22,759
as a doormat to trample on.

238
00:14:22,919 --> 00:14:23,440
Isn't that right?

239
00:14:23,679 --> 00:14:24,320
No.

240
00:14:24,559 --> 00:14:25,919
No, no!

241
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:27,120
Xiang Xiang! Xiang Xiang!

242
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:28,519
Don't listen to his nonsense.

243
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:30,000
Don't listen to his crap!

244
00:14:30,159 --> 00:14:31,200
I love you so much.

245
00:14:31,759 --> 00:14:32,559
Shut up!

246
00:14:33,639 --> 00:14:35,279
Liu Xiang was such a fine doctor.

247
00:14:35,919 --> 00:14:37,799
She could've had a brilliant life,

248
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:40,360
with friends, dreams, and a career.

249
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:43,000
Now trash like you has ruined it all.

250
00:14:43,799 --> 00:14:45,240
It wasn't me! It wasn't me!

251
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:47,159
It was her! She destroyed my home!

252
00:14:47,159 --> 00:14:48,720
She destroyed your home?

253
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:50,399
You wanna know

254
00:14:50,399 --> 00:14:52,960
who Liu Xiang's so-called toy boy is?

255
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:54,960
No...

256
00:14:56,519 --> 00:14:57,159
You two...

257
00:14:57,759 --> 00:14:59,399
Are you two trying to humiliate me?

258
00:15:04,559 --> 00:15:06,679
You read her chats and transfer records,

259
00:15:06,679 --> 00:15:08,000
and decided she had someone on the side.

260
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:10,480
Why didn't you bother to verify it?

261
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,320
You know Shen Qing, right?

262
00:15:13,559 --> 00:15:14,600
Liu Xiang's close friend.

263
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:16,240
Yes, that's right.

264
00:15:16,320 --> 00:15:17,720
I saw the transfer records.

265
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:20,559
I saw the transfers to her secret man!

266
00:15:20,919 --> 00:15:22,600
She's the one who betrayed me!

267
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:26,279
Shen Qing. Shen Qing is her bestie.
